=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Acknowledgement</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Dear {{ $json["issuedToName"] }},</p>
    <p>We acknowledge the importance of ensuring the safety and well-being of everyone involved in the construction process, including workers and the surrounding community. Our initial assessment conducted on {{ $json["createdDate"] }} for {{ $json["projectName"] }} identified certain areas that required corrective measures to mitigate potential health risks. However, we have observed that the recommended actions have not been executed as anticipated, leading to an incomplete assessment report. Five days have lapsed without the close out being received.</p>
    <p>To view the outstanding notices, click on this link:<br>
    {{ $json["nidLinks"] }}</p>
    <p>Best Regards,</p>
</body>
</html>

