    <title>Email Further Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Dear {{ $json["issuedToName"] }},</p>
    <p>We are writing to provide a further reminder regarding the pending corrective action for the Safety Inspection that was done on the {{ $json["createdDate"] }} that needs to be completed for the {{ $json["projectName"] }} construction project. As you are aware, this is the third reminder after 9 days without a close-out. It is crucial that we address these concerns promptly. By taking the necessary corrective action, we can ensure a safer environment and minimize any potential risk associated with the construction activities on your site.</p>
    <p>To view the outstanding notices, click on this link:<br>
    {{ $json["nidLinks"] }}</p>
    <p>Best Regards,</p>
</body>
</html>

