    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Escalation Email Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Please note, an escalation email could not be sent for Site Notice {{ $json["ownedSnid"] }} ({{ $json["projectName"] }}) as there are no external recipients specified in the email distribution list.</p>
    <p>Please contact Admin to assign external recipients to the email distribution list for future email escalation emails to be sent.</p>
    <p>Regards,</p>
    <p>Cairnmead Automation</p>
</body>
</html>
